```
function Test(){
    if( user not on mobile &amp;&amp; showAlert(&quot;Are you sure?&quot;){
         Logger.log(&quot;User says Yes&quot;);
    }
}
```

Is this possible? Or can I wait for 1 minute, if there&#39;s no response from the user, skip the alert and continue with other code?


